descriptionHtml:
This Mod adds 6 brand new Conjuration Spells. They are very balanced so it\'s not like cheating.
You will find them in Winterhold, in front of the Academy(screenshot).

The Mod includes the following Spells:

-Conjure Dwarven Spider: Novice
-Conjure Falmer: Apprentice
-Conjure Troll: Apprentice
-Conjure Frost Troll: Adept
-Conjure Dwarven Sphere: Adept
-Conjure Dwarven Centurion Master: Expert

Version: 1.0

If you like this mod, or if you find any bugs please leave a comment.
You can also check our my other mods, I\'m going to upload a big spellpack soon wich includes about 25 Spells so please stay tuned.

Have fun!
author: T3rRoR_SoLdi3R
